WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 25=

02:28.070 --> 02:29.630
Yan Zhang, it was you.

03:43.620 --> 03:44.460
Actually,

03:47.270 --> 03:49.230
I was never going to tell.

04:17.030 --> 04:18.470
One day,

04:20.230 --> 04:21.070
Yan Ke,

04:24.230 --> 04:25.790
you too will die

04:27.260 --> 04:28.940
in the hands of the one you love.

04:46.150 --> 04:47.110
Bai Sanxing.

04:52.590 --> 04:53.430
Bai Sanxing.

05:14.420 --> 05:15.710
Did I tell you to kill him?

05:16.910 --> 05:17.910
Bai Sanxing is not yours

05:17.910 --> 05:18.750
to deal with.

05:40.990 --> 05:42.910
Yan Zhang, Vice Lord of Xuling Temple,

05:43.260 --> 05:45.180
harmed spirits and forged puppets,

05:45.380 --> 05:46.420
bringing ruin to the Void,

05:46.790 --> 05:48.550
and trespassed into the Prison,

05:49.150 --> 05:50.820
colluding with felon Bai Sanxing

05:50.820 --> 05:51.873
to plot against Her Grace.

05:52.230 --> 05:53.070
After investigation,

05:53.420 --> 05:54.670
the evidence is conclusive.

05:56.150 --> 05:57.710
The chief culprit, Yan Zhang,

05:58.420 --> 06:00.380
has been annihilated by Her Grace.

06:00.820 --> 06:03.500
Bai Sanxing has also been seized.

06:04.300 --> 06:05.140
From this day on,

06:05.550 --> 06:07.030
search all of the Void,

06:07.620 --> 06:08.940
and hunt down Yan's accomplices.

06:09.300 --> 06:11.500
Wipe out the remaining puppets

06:11.500 --> 06:12.500
as soon as possible.

06:13.180 --> 06:15.150
Any spirits who stir up trouble

06:15.820 --> 06:17.260
must also be punished by the law.

06:19.180 --> 06:20.940
Yes, Your Grace.

06:22.180 --> 06:23.020
Your Grace,

06:23.150 --> 06:24.790
how will you deal with Bai Sanxing?

06:25.260 --> 06:26.420
He swallowed so many brothers

06:26.570 --> 06:27.420
in my temple.

06:27.420 --> 06:28.830
He must die for this.

06:35.710 --> 06:37.060
Her Grace has a plan.

06:37.710 --> 06:38.550
But...

06:43.990 --> 06:44.940
If there's nothing else,

06:44.940 --> 06:45.940
you may leave for now.

06:47.260 --> 06:48.100
Yes.

06:52.990 --> 06:54.550
Go on, go on. Move.

06:56.180 --> 06:58.060
Who knew Yan Zhang was so cruel?

06:58.060 --> 06:58.900
Indeed.

07:31.940 --> 07:33.860
Your Grace, I seek audience.

07:35.380 --> 07:36.220
Enter.

07:42.300 --> 07:43.140
Yan,

07:44.300 --> 07:45.230
what brings you to me?

07:55.590 --> 07:56.430
Simu,

07:56.670 --> 07:58.230
Yan's rebellion is no small matter.

07:58.740 --> 08:00.500
She could never

08:00.500 --> 08:01.550
have done it alone.

08:01.910 --> 08:03.110
Though Jiang Ai worked with us

08:03.110 --> 08:04.500
in the ambush on Bai Sanxing,

08:04.860 --> 08:06.740
she still has ties to Bai Sanxing.

08:07.230 --> 08:08.070
Besides,

08:08.550 --> 08:09.910
her Vice Lord plotted against you.

08:10.590 --> 08:12.110
Could she truly know nothing of it?

08:15.110 --> 08:16.380
If you suspect Jiang Ai,

08:17.300 --> 08:18.590
go find proof.

08:19.470 --> 08:20.910
If you can find proof,

08:21.470 --> 08:22.990
I will judge it fairly.

08:25.030 --> 08:25.990
Pity, though, Yan Zhang

08:25.990 --> 08:27.420
has met annihilation.

08:27.940 --> 08:28.780
Otherwise,

08:28.990 --> 08:30.860
I could have learned much more.

08:31.300 --> 08:32.540
The situation was urgent then.

08:32.780 --> 08:34.430
In my haste, I killed her.

08:35.380 --> 08:36.220
It's okay.

08:38.140 --> 08:39.140
For 300 years,

08:40.110 --> 08:41.590
those who sought to kill me

08:41.590 --> 08:42.470
have been many.

08:42.780 --> 08:44.110
I'm used to it.

08:44.860 --> 08:45.900
Luckily, by my side

08:45.900 --> 08:46.900
are you and Jiang Ai.

08:47.430 --> 08:48.216
Otherwise,

08:48.227 --> 08:49.807
we wouldn't have taken them so easily.

08:51.710 --> 08:53.310
Thanks to your sound planning, Simu.

08:53.860 --> 08:55.230
I only followed the plan.

09:05.190 --> 09:06.103
There's one more thing.

09:06.500 --> 09:08.590
How will you deal with Bai Sanxing?

09:10.670 --> 09:11.520
Even the Prison

09:11.520 --> 09:13.190
could not destroy him in 300 years.

09:14.310 --> 09:15.500
I've found another place

09:15.500 --> 09:16.470
to hold him.

09:16.746 --> 09:17.782
But he's stirred rebellion

09:17.793 --> 09:18.660
time and again.

09:19.110 --> 09:20.350
We must root him out.

09:25.380 --> 09:27.140
You need not remind me of that.

09:30.860 --> 09:32.310
The chaos is not yet settled.

09:33.020 --> 09:34.660
Jiang Ai is badly hurt and bedridden.

09:35.310 --> 09:37.260
You must have a lot to deal with.

09:37.990 --> 09:39.140
Go attend to it first.

09:48.190 --> 09:49.030
Yes.

10:28.140 --> 10:29.070
Your Grace,

10:29.070 --> 10:30.430
the Left Hand is stable now.

10:30.710 --> 10:31.976
She still needs time to recover.

10:36.780 --> 10:37.620
Your Grace.

10:38.740 --> 10:39.580
How are you?

10:40.140 --> 10:42.020
My Vice Lord tried to kill you.

10:42.470 --> 10:43.470
I failed to see it

10:43.710 --> 10:44.660
and control her.

10:45.260 --> 10:46.380
Please punish me.

10:49.500 --> 10:50.340
Rather than that,

10:51.740 --> 10:52.830
I'm more curious

10:53.900 --> 10:55.430
about why you saved Bai Sanxing.

11:06.310 --> 11:07.430
Back then, Bai Sanxing

11:08.230 --> 11:09.860
locked me up and controlled me

11:09.860 --> 11:10.900
like a caged possession.

11:11.780 --> 11:12.620
I was never one

11:12.620 --> 11:14.190
to be manipulated.

11:15.020 --> 11:16.350
I hated him to the bone.

11:17.540 --> 11:18.710
For these 300 years,

11:18.710 --> 11:20.260
every time I thought of him,

11:20.990 --> 11:22.470
I wished I could

11:23.190 --> 11:24.380
hack him to pieces

11:24.620 --> 11:26.190
and be done with him for good.

11:27.540 --> 11:28.990
But at that very moment,

11:31.620 --> 11:33.190
I just couldn't stand by and watch him

11:33.190 --> 11:34.140
die before my very eyes.

11:36.620 --> 11:38.070
Deep down, you still care for him.

11:39.310 --> 11:40.590
You just will not admit it.

11:46.380 --> 11:47.230
Do not dwell on it.

11:48.540 --> 11:49.500
You've been badly hurt.

11:50.110 --> 11:50.950
Get some proper rest.

11:52.430 --> 11:53.270
Your Grace,

11:56.190 --> 11:57.030
how

11:58.900 --> 12:00.070
is he now?

12:00.990 --> 12:01.830
Still alive.

12:32.860 --> 12:33.700
Grand Ancestor.

12:35.380 --> 12:36.950
Grand Ancestor, long time no see.

12:37.110 --> 12:38.470
I thought you had forgotten me.

12:39.110 --> 12:39.990
In a few days,

12:41.070 --> 12:42.110
I will go to Nandu.

12:42.380 --> 12:43.220
Grand Ancestor,

12:43.710 --> 12:44.990
you are coming to Nandu?

12:52.580 --> 12:59.580
(Chamber of Buddha's Grace)

13:00.620 --> 13:01.470
We are going to visit

13:01.470 --> 13:02.310
my mother.

13:03.470 --> 13:04.380
She likes it quiet.

13:20.020 --> 13:20.990
Who is it?

13:24.950 --> 13:25.860
Xu.

13:30.470 --> 13:31.310
Mother,

13:32.900 --> 13:33.740
I'm back.

13:35.900 --> 13:37.780
You had a tiring journey yesterday.

13:38.540 --> 13:39.540
I only...

13:43.020 --> 13:43.900
Sit down.

13:43.900 --> 13:44.780
Go on, sit.

13:52.590 --> 13:53.620
This is...

13:54.946 --> 13:56.209
I took him in on the battlefield

13:56.220 --> 13:56.790
as my brother.

13:56.990 --> 13:57.830
He's Xue Chenying.

13:58.260 --> 13:59.140
He lost his parents.

13:59.900 --> 14:01.740
His sister earned great merit in battle.

14:02.470 --> 14:03.860
I promised her I'd look after him.

14:04.900 --> 14:05.740
Chenying,

14:06.830 --> 14:07.670
greet Mother.

14:13.380 --> 14:14.260
Greetings, Mrs. Duan.

14:16.260 --> 14:17.100
Child,

14:17.740 --> 14:19.070
no need for such a grand bow.

14:19.830 --> 14:21.260
That you came here

14:21.260 --> 14:22.190
is fate in itself.

14:23.190 --> 14:24.143
The Buddha is merciful.

14:24.660 --> 14:25.500
This place

14:26.190 --> 14:27.470
will be your home.

14:52.430 --> 14:54.230
Here, have some pastries.

14:54.660 --> 14:55.500
Thank you.

15:01.230 --> 15:02.070
Chenying,

15:06.540 --> 15:07.380
go on, eat.

15:14.386 --> 15:15.540
Mother, whenever you see me,

15:15.540 --> 15:16.600
you're always so reserved.

15:16.870 --> 15:18.039
Jingyuan may start to suspect

15:18.050 --> 15:19.183
there is discord between us.

15:21.830 --> 15:22.990
I only feel

15:23.740 --> 15:25.693
that all these years,
I've done nothing for you.

15:26.470 --> 15:28.430
After all, when you needed me most,

15:29.780 --> 15:31.190
I could not stay by your side.

15:42.430 --> 15:43.370
You're overthinking it.

15:45.900 --> 15:46.740
As for this matter,

15:48.590 --> 15:49.780
I've never blamed you.

15:51.260 --> 15:53.470
That's exactly why

15:54.110 --> 15:55.660
I feel even worse inside.

15:56.950 --> 15:58.110
I can't face you.

16:07.380 --> 16:08.380
Perhaps my parents

16:09.990 --> 16:10.990
had something

16:11.860 --> 16:12.860
they truly sought.

16:15.260 --> 16:16.260
Even blood kin,

16:17.660 --> 16:18.660
in their eyes,

16:19.900 --> 16:20.990
meant very little.

16:23.830 --> 16:24.950
I do not think that is right,

16:26.430 --> 16:27.500
yet I understand them.

16:31.830 --> 16:32.710
If only Xiaoxiao

16:32.710 --> 16:33.620
were here now.

16:36.900 --> 16:37.740
Why?

16:37.950 --> 16:40.110
Because she'd surely comfort you,

16:40.500 --> 16:41.830
and ease your sorrow.

16:53.310 --> 16:54.150
It is all right.

16:54.740 --> 16:55.950
I am not too upset.

16:56.740 --> 16:57.780
But I still hope for her

16:58.500 --> 16:59.540
to come here,

17:21.910 --> 17:22.750
Simu.

17:23.470 --> 17:25.060
Why must we come here?

19:20.670 --> 19:21.510
Simu,

19:23.663 --> 19:24.956
you grew up in the Mortal World.

19:25.460 --> 19:26.300
You have always liked

19:26.300 --> 19:27.580
its bustling liveliness,

19:28.060 --> 19:29.633
instead of the cold silence of the Void.

19:31.710 --> 19:32.910
If you like,

19:33.540 --> 19:34.540
we can make the Void

19:34.540 --> 19:35.820
vivid and lively

19:36.500 --> 19:37.470
like the Mortal World.

19:39.780 --> 19:40.620
Yan,

19:41.780 --> 19:43.150
you're just trying to cheer me up.

19:44.797 --> 19:47.023
The Void is at the bottom of the sea,
without daylight.

19:47.260 --> 19:48.580
How could it ever be lively?

19:50.150 --> 19:51.300
If you want,

19:51.950 --> 19:53.230
I will do everything I can

19:53.580 --> 19:54.420
to make it happen.

20:07.910 --> 20:08.750
Simu,

20:10.580 --> 20:11.820
I have a gift for you.

20:18.990 --> 20:19.830
I know

20:20.540 --> 20:21.910
that you never wanted to be

20:23.300 --> 20:24.390
the Sovereign of Spirits,

20:24.390 --> 20:25.796
bound by the Void's endless affairs.

20:26.990 --> 20:28.500
I will guard the Void for you.

20:30.100 --> 20:31.106
Those who stand above all

20:31.430 --> 20:32.390
often walk alone.

20:33.190 --> 20:34.150
But you have me.

20:34.740 --> 20:35.910
I'll always stay by your side.

20:40.100 --> 20:41.235
I've bound my vital gate

20:41.246 --> 20:42.150
to this hairpin.

20:43.430 --> 20:44.430
Now, I give it to you.

20:45.540 --> 20:46.820
This is my heart's vow.

20:49.100 --> 20:50.020
If you are willing,

20:50.950 --> 20:52.580
I will be yours forever.

20:53.150 --> 20:54.076
I'll forever love you,

20:54.710 --> 20:56.100
be your friend,

20:56.540 --> 20:57.390
your lover,

20:58.500 --> 20:59.430
and your Yan.

21:03.150 --> 21:03.990
Simu.

21:14.020 --> 21:15.260
I'm sorry, Yan.

21:16.300 --> 21:17.260
I can't say yes.

21:19.990 --> 21:21.430
You're the partner I trust most.

21:22.820 --> 21:23.660
That is all.

21:29.910 --> 21:30.750
Simu, you...

21:32.500 --> 21:33.990
Are you truly turning me down?

21:39.356 --> 21:40.352
If you don't want it now,

21:40.363 --> 21:41.140
that's all right.

21:41.360 --> 21:42.230
I can keep it for you.

21:42.230 --> 21:43.070
Yan,

21:44.300 --> 21:45.640
Jiang Ai's wound is nearly healed.

21:45.870 --> 21:46.990
She can resume duty tomorrow.

21:47.630 --> 21:48.992
I'll leave the Void's daily affairs

21:49.003 --> 21:49.540
to you both.

21:50.430 --> 21:51.540
I need to go to Nandu.

21:51.780 --> 21:52.620
Simu,

21:56.060 --> 21:57.020
I don't want you to go.

21:58.470 --> 22:00.470
Whatever it is, I'll go for you.

22:07.630 --> 22:08.470
Yan Ke,

22:15.230 --> 22:16.070
you have overstepped.

22:26.190 --> 22:27.030
Overstepped?

22:29.020 --> 22:31.150
I kept too strictly

22:31.382 --> 22:32.592
to the proper code between us,

22:32.603 --> 22:33.420
so you neglected me.

22:33.420 --> 22:34.340
I never neglected you.

22:34.500 --> 22:36.020
You are my most trusted Right Hand.

22:43.990 --> 22:44.950
When I am away,

22:45.820 --> 22:47.340
the Void relies on you and Jiang Ai.

22:48.500 --> 22:49.910
As for what you said just now,

22:50.870 --> 22:52.260
I will pretend I never heard it.

24:03.786 --> 24:04.852
Greetings, Grand Ancestor.

24:08.190 --> 24:10.230
Grand Ancestor.

24:14.910 --> 24:15.950
Grand Ancestor.

24:25.990 --> 24:27.500
To welcome me,

24:27.910 --> 24:29.430
you even dressed up.

24:40.190 --> 24:41.150
Grand Ancestor,

24:43.020 --> 24:43.860
may I

24:45.990 --> 24:47.820
shake your hand just once?

24:52.390 --> 24:53.990
It is not as if we have never met.

24:54.390 --> 24:55.470
No need to be so formal.

24:57.540 --> 24:59.500
That was in my childhood.

25:00.150 --> 25:01.300
I only remember

25:02.020 --> 25:04.020
you holding me back then.

25:27.580 --> 25:29.150
It still feels the same.

25:56.910 --> 25:58.020
You've rarely had the chance

25:58.020 --> 25:58.950
to come to Nandu.

25:59.190 --> 26:00.190
Would you like

26:00.340 --> 26:01.580
to go check on Duan Xu?

26:02.780 --> 26:03.630
I have no time.

26:04.230 --> 26:05.780
General Duan hasn't been

26:05.910 --> 26:07.260
having an easy time lately.

26:07.500 --> 26:08.950
I heard his family is choosing

26:08.950 --> 26:10.100
a bride for him these days.

26:10.300 --> 26:11.470
Perhaps before long,

26:11.470 --> 26:12.630
he will be married.

26:18.300 --> 26:19.190
What is that to me?

26:27.950 --> 26:28.990
Grand Ancestor,

26:29.390 --> 26:30.580
if he truly takes a wife,

26:30.710 --> 26:31.780
you will lose him.

26:31.780 --> 26:33.100
Doesn't this sadden you?

26:33.670 --> 26:34.910
Duan Xu is a mortal.

26:35.530 --> 26:36.390
Starting a family

26:36.390 --> 26:37.820
is the most natural thing for him.

26:39.390 --> 26:40.670
Why should I feel sad?

26:41.060 --> 26:42.820
Isn't he your spell bearer?

26:42.820 --> 26:44.190
Don't you find it a pity?

26:46.300 --> 26:47.116
If he's still willing

26:47.127 --> 26:48.230
to trade his senses with me,

26:48.430 --> 26:49.670
the arrangement between us

26:49.670 --> 26:50.820
will continue as before.

26:51.950 --> 26:53.190
What is there to regret?

26:53.780 --> 26:55.030
- But…
- Enough.

26:55.630 --> 26:57.500
I came for serious matters.

26:58.630 --> 27:00.020
Spare me nonsense.

27:05.340 --> 27:07.260
Last time, you asked me

27:07.390 --> 27:08.820
to make a magical artifact.

27:09.020 --> 27:09.860
I was...

27:10.020 --> 27:11.910
It is late. You should sleep now.

27:14.230 --> 27:15.910
Grand Ancestor is here tonight.

27:16.150 --> 27:17.430
We're having a meeting.

27:18.707 --> 27:19.547
Leave it to tomorrow.

27:19.558 --> 27:21.642
(Ziji, Hejia Fengyi's maid)
Considering your health,

27:21.652 --> 27:22.839
you should be asleep now.

27:26.540 --> 27:27.500
Your Grand Ancestor

27:28.820 --> 27:30.190
also wishes you a longer life.

27:37.100 --> 27:37.940
It's all right.

27:39.150 --> 27:40.060
Let's talk tomorrow.

27:41.870 --> 27:43.230
Don't you wish to know

27:43.230 --> 27:44.950
which young ladies the Duan clan chose?

27:44.950 --> 27:45.790
I do not.

28:04.670 --> 28:06.063
Your Grace, I'll arrange your rest.

28:06.230 --> 28:07.070
Please come with me.

28:20.630 --> 28:22.740
Fragrance pouch! Trinkets!

28:23.150 --> 28:23.990
Xu,

28:24.580 --> 28:25.420
I don't think

28:25.430 --> 28:26.770
the girls Father picked for you

28:27.260 --> 28:28.100
are very pretty.

28:28.580 --> 28:30.580
You're too brilliant.

28:31.230 --> 28:32.070
How about this?

28:32.300 --> 28:33.710
You stroll the streets,

28:34.100 --> 28:35.190
seeking romance.

28:35.390 --> 28:36.230
What do you say?

28:37.430 --> 28:38.300
Stop talking nonsense.

28:39.190 --> 28:40.190
How is that nonsense?

28:40.950 --> 28:42.020
Fang Xianye

28:42.020 --> 28:43.390
is only good at studying.

28:43.580 --> 28:44.420
It's nothing special.

28:44.870 --> 28:46.020
But you can write essays

28:46.500 --> 28:48.540
to steady the realm

28:48.780 --> 28:51.060
and fight on the battlefield.

28:52.060 --> 28:52.900
How about I

28:53.430 --> 28:54.270
seek a fine match

28:54.470 --> 28:55.670
for you today?

28:55.670 --> 28:56.510
What do you think?

28:56.820 --> 28:58.500
What kind of lady do you like?

29:03.500 --> 29:05.190
I like...

29:08.150 --> 29:09.230
I like

29:10.500 --> 29:11.780
a lady not found in this world.

29:15.710 --> 29:16.630
Fine.

29:16.630 --> 29:18.470
Then I'll go make a wish.

29:19.340 --> 29:20.780
I'll wish for Goddess Chang'e

29:21.150 --> 29:23.060
to come down and find you.

29:24.260 --> 29:25.100
All right.

29:25.230 --> 29:26.190
With your sincere heart,

29:26.740 --> 29:28.670
your prayer may come true.

29:29.390 --> 29:30.950
Xu, be serious, will you?

29:32.300 --> 29:34.980
(Lotusborn Pavilion)

29:39.470 --> 29:40.310
Xu,

29:40.910 --> 29:42.630
you're really not coming in with me?

29:44.060 --> 29:44.900
Go in by yourself.

29:47.740 --> 29:48.580
All right then.

29:57.190 --> 29:58.500
Everyone, please wait a moment.

29:58.710 --> 30:00.100
The Prophet will soon arrive

30:00.230 --> 30:02.260
to burn prayer paper for you all

30:02.260 --> 30:03.710
and present blessed flowers.

30:08.740 --> 30:09.580
This is

30:11.430 --> 30:13.150
the soul candle from the Prison.

30:13.820 --> 30:14.670
Grand Ancestor,

30:15.260 --> 30:16.910
you came for this matter?

30:17.740 --> 30:18.580
That's right.

30:21.470 --> 30:22.950
Could the magical artifact

30:24.100 --> 30:25.670
you asked for…

30:28.540 --> 30:29.630
300 years have passed.

30:32.260 --> 30:34.260
It's time to end this.

30:40.260 --> 30:41.466
Only those in the Mortal World

30:45.300 --> 30:46.430
can grasp its affairs.

30:52.260 --> 30:58.120
♪Touched memories linger like shadows♪

30:58.120 --> 31:02.580
(Lotusborn Pavilion)

31:04.850 --> 31:10.860
♪If I could softly call you like this♪

31:11.950 --> 31:16.000
♪As gentle as a fleeting embrace♪

31:16.020 --> 31:17.150
So, this is what mortals call

31:17.150 --> 31:18.163
the bustle of mortal life.

31:18.430 --> 31:19.710
It really is a mix of scents.

31:20.100 --> 31:21.100
I can smell everything.

31:22.100 --> 31:22.940
Foxy,

31:23.430 --> 31:24.870
just let me have a taste.

31:24.880 --> 31:29.950
♪A lifetime is given
for a name to be remembered♪

31:30.480 --> 31:33.840
♪There are passions and pains♪

31:34.040 --> 31:36.940
♪Hope we'll experience them together♪

31:37.620 --> 31:42.310
♪Before we forget or grow apart♪

31:42.340 --> 31:43.180
Simu.

31:44.470 --> 31:45.310
Simu.

31:46.990 --> 31:47.830
What are you doing?

31:47.920 --> 31:49.570
♪Grows dim and fades away♪

31:49.570 --> 31:51.320
♪What would come of it?♪

31:51.340 --> 31:52.180
Sorry

31:53.260 --> 31:54.100
for my rudeness.

31:54.310 --> 31:55.960
♪I'll come near and run to you♪

31:55.960 --> 31:59.140
♪To heal the deepest wounds♪

31:59.660 --> 32:02.350
♪Miracles, eternity, and radiance♪

32:02.350 --> 32:05.100
♪Worth more than any barren land♪

32:05.200 --> 32:07.700
♪I might as well
spend the rest of my life♪

32:07.700 --> 32:11.670
♪Walking with you through eternity♪

32:30.630 --> 32:31.780
It's the smell of rain.

32:33.060 --> 32:34.390
Rain carries the scent of the sky

32:35.230 --> 32:36.430
and draws out the earth's scent

32:37.540 --> 32:38.390
and the vitality

32:38.390 --> 32:39.630
of all living things.

32:40.690 --> 32:43.990
♪I'd bear your feelings♪

32:44.000 --> 32:44.930
How wonderful.

32:45.310 --> 32:47.080
♪I'm blessed to have met you♪

32:47.080 --> 32:49.720
♪Then I won't let you go♪

32:50.060 --> 32:52.350
♪I wish I could be a firework♪

32:52.350 --> 32:56.670
♪To burn out for the moment you turn♪

33:24.081 --> 33:29.411
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

33:29.741 --> 33:33.991
♪Light encountered shadow♪

33:35.351 --> 33:40.721
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

33:41.021 --> 33:45.621
♪The unbreakable fate♪

33:46.711 --> 33:48.551
♪Suddenly cracked♪

34:00.761 --> 34:06.201
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

34:06.381 --> 34:10.711
♪Light encountered shadow♪

34:12.081 --> 34:17.471
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

34:17.701 --> 34:21.641
♪The unbreakable fate♪

34:23.411 --> 34:25.301
♪Suddenly cracked♪

34:27.961 --> 34:31.121
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

34:31.121 --> 34:33.651
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

34:33.651 --> 34:39.171
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

34:39.171 --> 34:42.411
♪Following fate's guidance♪

34:42.411 --> 34:47.271
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

34:47.611 --> 34:50.631
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

34:50.631 --> 34:53.451
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

34:53.711 --> 34:56.241
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

34:56.241 --> 35:01.661
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

35:01.831 --> 35:04.901
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

35:05.061 --> 35:09.961
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

35:10.171 --> 35:13.641
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
